author: rhuijben
msg: (write_symlink): Switch to a baton type that is just the output path.
(init_patch_target): Just write the patch on the temporary location,
instead of trying to overwrite the target directly.
(apply_one_patch): Don't try to close handles that aren't set.

author: rhuijben
msg: Fix yet another issue in the patch_change_symlink_target test, and create
another test based upon the error we had in this test.
(patch_change_symlink_target): Not only did the file names not match, the
file body didn't match either. This makes the test succeed on systems
without symlink support. Verify if the final node type matches to
fail on more error cases without attempting to verify the link yet.
(single_line_mismatch): New XFail test which shows that currently a non
matching line patch deletes the target.
